<figureCitation box="[159,225,1183,1208]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="2.[151,250,1757,1779]" captionTargetBox="[152,1435,193,1732]" captionTargetId="figure@2.[151,1436,193,1736]" captionTargetPageId="2" captionText="FIGURE 1. Colletes comaticus Kuhlmann, sp. nov., male: a. specimen, lateral view; b. gonostylus (lateral view); c. metasomal sternum 7 (dorsal view). C. bernadettae Kuhlmann 2000, male: d. metasomal sternum 7 (dorsal view). C. comatus Noskiewicz 1936, male: e. metasomal sternum 7 (dorsal view). C. comatoides Kuhlmann &amp; Proshchalykin 2013, male: f. metasomal sternum 7 (dorsal view). Scale bar: 1 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/239795/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="82">
